Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每次下大雨\N我都会想起这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,暴风雨\N和朋友太太单独相处之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我两个月前离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为了帮我庆生 \N朋友夫妻来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,下这么大的雨\N还来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本来和他约好在车站等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他说会晚点来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,会感冒啊\N进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友的太太 秋子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很温柔\N年纪比我大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说对她没有好感\N当然是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,会感冒吧\N去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雨伞这边可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我拿吧\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,佑太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没有热水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看瓦斯管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,去外面看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好像瓦斯管破了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是男生一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我收到的尾牙礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是幸苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,时间会解决一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是最后的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一起用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很冷哦\N会感冒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以问一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和我聊一聊\N会比较轻松哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都可以说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其实。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太太外遇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,佑太很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是你太太不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子也很温柔耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的太太\N真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公也是成天忙工作\N很晚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道在外面搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我老公是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来帮你庆生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,佑太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被你讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被你讨厌就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以吧 这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,知道这样不可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以舔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.60,0:24:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.80,0:25:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.60,0:26:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要脱了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.30,0:26:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样脱不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.40,0:26:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让我多摸一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.80,0:26:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.20,0:26:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.30,0:27:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.50,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.30,0:28:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.90,0:28:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.30,0:32:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.30,0:33:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.10,0:33:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.20,0:35:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧 秋子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.60,0:36:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也帮我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.40,0:39:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.10,0:39:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.00,0:40:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.30,0:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.20,0:42:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.00,0:43:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.30,0:44:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看着喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.40,0:44:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.30,0:44:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.20,0:47:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.30,0:49:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗\N好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.00,0:49:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.00,0:49:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.40,0:52:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.00,0:53:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.60,0:53:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.30,0:54:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.20,0:57:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.20,0:58:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.70,0:58:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N我还在公司
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.90,0:58:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还要花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.80,0:58:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为雨太大了\N所以我还在家
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.60,0:58:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.30,0:58:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在跟你说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.40,0:58:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.30,0:58:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法控制此时的我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.30,1:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.80,1:00:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室还像可以用了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.20,1:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.30,1:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.30,1:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服也干了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.10,1:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样应该好了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.80,1:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好了\N热的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.40,1:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，又弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.00,1:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.60,1:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.00,1:01:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒喔
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.20,1:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.40,1:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.40,1:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我射了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.20,1:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.30,1:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.60,1:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,电车发动了 我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.80,1:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不能去他家了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.70,1:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.30,1:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.80,1:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他要回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.60,1:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也该走了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.80,1:19:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要走吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.80,1:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这场雨不停就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.30,1:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.80,1:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.00,1:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.50,1:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚还可以
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.00,1:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.60,1:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.60,1:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还在下雨 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.60,1:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.00,1:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.80,1:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,秋子没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.00,1:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我又弄湿了
